<item>
            <title>[LU-19209] ofd_access_log_reader should state how to enable access logs</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19209</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;ofd access logs are not enabled by default; they are enabled by setting the size of the circular buffer they require.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Someone unfamiliar with ofd access logs and the reader may not know this.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;State how to enable the logs in the usage message of ofd_access_log_reader, and in the comment of the source file implementing them, so users need not spelunk through code to learn how.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
